

1 K g Paul ab si ha neid g e jehnitiddam ch hab kaij, “Ni‑hajuni, chum ani hekid si ni‑nakog mant am hab wo waꞌi junihid g s‑apꞌekam ch hab pi wo shaꞌi haꞌichukaj si has ni‑elidad am tahgio g Jiosh ia i himdam tashkaj.” 2 Kut hegai uhgchu pahl mash hab chehgig Ananias am ha cheha hegam mo an miabidch gegok mat ab wo si shonihi g Paul chinij ab. T ab shonihi. 

3 K hab kaij g Paul, “Jiosh at hemho ab wo wa uhpam i nodagi ihda am m‑wui ahpi map s‑chu iattomk. Ab ap dak ch ni‑lodait g t‑chehanigkaj ch eda ep melchkwuhim g t‑chehanig map ab ha chehani mat ab wo ni‑shonihi.” 

4 K hab kaij hegam mo an miabidch gegok g Paul, “S‑koꞌokam ap has ahg g uhgchu pahl.” 

5 K hab kaij g Paul, “Ni‑hajuni, mant hems wo s‑mahchk mokis d uhgchu pahl, nt pi hab wo shaꞌi chei, no pi hab chuꞌig g Jiosh oꞌohana: 

Pi g am wo shaꞌi pi ap has ahgad g e‑geꞌejig.” *Exodus 22:28 * 

6 K hegam e jehnigiddam haꞌi d Sajusi ch haꞌi ep d Palasi. T id am i s‑mai g Paul k am si s‑kaidam neok ha wui ch hab kaij, “Ni‑hajuni, ahni ani d Palasi ch d ha amjedkam g Palasi ch ha wepo s‑wohochud mat g koꞌi ep wo i wuwha ab hihaꞌini t amjed. Kum heg hekaj ni‑lodait.” 7 T id am i kah g e jehnigiddam k am ha hekaj aꞌai e neꞌowin k pi ab hu i e wehmt. 8 Hegam mo d Sajusi o pi ab hu wohochud mat g koꞌi wo i wuwha ab hihaꞌini t amjed ch ep pi wohochud mo an haꞌichug g anghil o g kokꞌoi. K wabshaba g Palasi wehs s‑wohochud ihda. 

9 T am hahawa i si e gewkai g ha‑hihinki. T am haꞌi gegokiwua hegam mo d chehanig hudawogam ch d Palasi k am si s‑gewkam ha shohbid k hab kaij, “Pi att haꞌichu shaꞌi cheh mas pi ap hab juh ihda oꞌodham. Tp hems wa woho g anghil am wehmaj neo.” 

10 T am baꞌich i si e gewkai g ha‑neꞌowina. Kum hab e ahg mat am hu wo wantsh g Paul. K g shondal ha‑geꞌejig am hahawa ha chehani g e‑shondalig mat am wo ha wohppoꞌi. Kut am hihim k be k ged i bei e‑kih wui. 

11 Sh am baꞌich d i hudunk, tsh am i e chehgi g Jesus Paul wui k hab kaij, “Ia ap si s‑mahch ch am ahgahim haꞌichu ab ni‑amjed. Kuni am i m‑gewkemhun mapt hab wo wa masma hab e juh am Rome t am.” 

**Matsh g Paul wehm oꞌodham wo s‑muꞌam **

12 K am baꞌich d i tash wabsh i siꞌalim, tsh am haꞌi e hemapai g Tutuligo k am chum Jiosh tahgio aꞌai si e ahgid mat pi haꞌichu wo hug k hoꞌip mua g Paul. 13 Kush i baꞌiwechkim giꞌikko wehst‑mahm idam matsh hab masma e apꞌech. 14 Tsh am hahawa hihi ha wui g uꞌugchu papal ch geꞌeged ch hab kaij, “Matt am Jiosh tahgio aꞌai si t‑ahgi matt pi haꞌichu wo hug k hoꞌip mua hegai Paul. 15 Kumt ahpim g e jehnigiddam ha wehm am wo ahgi g shondal ha‑geꞌejig mat ab wo i bek g Paul em‑wui. Kumt hab wo e wuad mam baꞌich haꞌichu s‑mahchimk ab amjed. Kutt ahchim wo t‑nahtokchid matt wo mua mat koi ia hu wo jiwia em‑wui.” 

16 Tsh wabshaba g Paul cheoj maꞌi am i kah ihda k am him k am i wah shondal ha‑kih ed k am ahgid g Paul. 17 Tsh heg am hema wai g shondal ha‑geꞌejig k hab kaij ab wui, “Am g behꞌi ihda wechij oꞌodham am si uhgchu shondal ha‑geꞌejig wui, matsh wo haꞌichu ahgi.” 

18 Tsh wa woho am i bei wui k hab kaij, “Ihda wechij oꞌodham at ia jiwia k am nei hegai Paul mo ia e kuhpch. T heg am ni‑waid k hab ni‑ahg mant ab wo i bei m‑wui matsh wo haꞌichu m‑ahgi.” 

19 Tsh g si uhgchu ha‑geꞌejig ab bei nowij an k gam hu hekelko i wanimed k ab kakke, “Shahchu apt wo ni‑ahgi?” 

20 K hab kaij, “Ni‑wehm oꞌodham at am i e apꞌech matsh siꞌalim ab wo m‑tai mamt am wo i bei g Paul e jehnigiddam ha wui hab wabsh s‑e junimk mat am baꞌich haꞌichu wo i s‑mai ab amjed. 21 Pt wabshaba pi ab hu wo ha kaiha. Giꞌikko wehst‑mahm i baꞌiwechkim chechoj atsh am wo e eꞌestok ch wo kihshad nat pi am chum Jiosh tahgio aꞌai si e ahgi matsh pi haꞌichu wo hug k hoꞌip mua g Paul. K hemuch e nahtokch mat am hab wo e juh ch wabsh nenida mapt has wo e juh.” 

22 Sh hab kaij g si ha‑uhgchuga, “Pi g am hedai shaꞌi ahgid hegai mapt haschu ia ni‑ahgi.” Tsh gam hu hahawa hih g Paul maꞌi. 

**Mamtsh gam hu bek g Paul Cesaria wui **

23 Tsh g si uhgchu shondal ha‑geꞌejig gohk am ha wai g ha‑geꞌegeꞌejig k hab kaij, “Am g wo haꞌi i ha gawulkad gohk siant shondal ch wewaꞌakko wehst‑mahm ehp mo g kakawyu ha chehchej ch gohk siant ehp mo s‑e mahch ab is‑pahyo t ab. Kut hegam wo e nahtok ch wo hihi mat d wo i humukt ohlak chuhug am Cesaria kihhim wui. 24 Kumt am haꞌi wo i ha apꞌech g kakawyu mat g Paul wo hekaj. Mt am s‑ap wo i be k am wo uꞌapa heg wui geꞌe kownal mo d Felix.” 25 Neh, bash kaij ch am hahawa oꞌohani hegai uhgchu kownal ihda: 

26 “Ab g i s‑ni‑hoꞌigeꞌid ahpi uhgchu ni‑kownalig Felix. Am ant wo m‑oꞌohani ahni mani d Claudius Lysius 27 nat pi g geꞌe haꞌichu has e juh. Tutuligo at am wabsh hema si be k chum alo mua. Kunt s‑mai mo ihda ab uꞌukch g e‑shel hab masma mo g Rome t am kihkam. Kutt hekaj g ni‑shondalig ha wehm am doꞌibia. 28 Nt amjed am i bei Tutuligo e jehnigiddam ha wui s‑mahchimk hegai mam haschu ab abchud. 29 Kuki wabshaba pi am hu d shai hegai mas hekaj wo e muhkid o wo e kuhpach. Heg amki ab waꞌi abchud mat g hejel ha‑chehanig melchkwua. 30 Sh am hahawa haꞌi e nakog idam Tutuligo matsh wo mua. Kunt am ha hekaj ha cheha g ni‑shondalig mat ab m‑wui wo bei. Kuni hab ha ahg hegam mo ab haꞌichu abchud mat ahpi m‑wui wo gagda. Neh, id o wud waꞌi.” 

31 Tsh am hab e juh g shondal hegai mam haschu ab i ha chehani k am i bei g Paul chuhug ch ed k am uꞌapa Antipatris kihhim t am. 32 Sh am baꞌich d i tash, tsh hegam shondal mo wabsh e‑tahtadkaj hihim gam hu uhpam hihi Jerusalem wui. 33 Tsh hegam mo shoshoigakch am i bei Cesaria wui k am dada k am i mah g kownal g oꞌohana k ab wui hahawa i dagito g Paul. 

34 Tsh g kownal am neꞌokchul hegai oꞌohana k ab kakke g Paul mas haschu jewed amjed. Sh heg am ahgid mo ab Cilicia jewed amjed. 35 Sh hab kaij ab wui, “M ant wo wa m‑nei mat hekid wo dada hegam mo ab haꞌichu m‑abchud.” Sh g shondaligaj am hahawa nuhkud kownal kih ed. 

